Package: ttcurate
Title: What the Package Does
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jon", "Harmon", , "jonthegeek@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4781-4346"))
Description: Helper functions and guidance for curating datasets for the
    'TidyTuesday' weekly data project. 'TidyTuesday' is a project by the
    'Data Science Learning Community' in which they post a weekly dataset
    in a public data repository
    (<https://github.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday>) for people to
    analyze and visualize. This package includes tools to explore past
    submissions, analyze dataset sizes, and follow best practices for data
    preparation and documentation.
